snippet.title: Babies and kids are really funny and make us laugh - Funny baby & kid compilation
snippet.description:
Babies and kids make us laugh on every step of their way, they are so adorable, cute and funny! Just look how all these babies, toddlers and kids dance, laugh, fail, get along with dogs, sleep,... What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
